trans-unit.source: Provides access to add attributes for one specific type to one specific <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gir tilgang til å legge til attributter for en bestemt til én bestemt <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> is queried for attributes for a type, if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> was populated using <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> for that type, the delegate is passed a AttributeCallbackBuilder.
trans-unit.target: Første gang en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>forespørres for attributter for typen hvis den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>ble fylles ut med <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>for denne typen representanten sendes en AttributeCallbackBuilder.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> removes the callback reference and adds any attribute information provided by calls to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>fjerner tilbakeringing referansen og legger til attributtinformasjon fra kall til <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to the attribute table that created this builder.
trans-unit.target: Legger til innholdet i de angitte attributtene i tabellen attributtet som opprettet denne builder.

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the table, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en attributtet er i konflikt med et annet attributt allerede inkludert i tabellen, erstatter attributtet siste legges til forrige attributter.

trans-unit.source: Attributes can be added only to the type specified by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Attributter kan legges bare til typen som er angitt av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The attributes that are added to the table.
trans-unit.target: Attributtene som er lagt til i tabellen.
